title: BRIEF-Park National Reports Q1 EPS Of $2.02
text:
April 20, 2018 / 8:19 PM / Updated 3 minutes ago BRIEF-Park National Reports Q1 EPS Of $2.02 Reuters Staff 
April 20 (Reuters) - Park National Corp: 
* REPORTS INCREASED NET INCOME IN FIRST QUARTER 2018 FINANCIAL RESULTS AND RAISES QUARTERLY DIVIDEND * Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE $2.02 
* Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $1.63 â€” THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S 
* BOARD OF DIRECTORS INCREASED QUARTERLY CASH DIVIDEND FROM $0.94 PER COMMON SHARE TO $0.96 PER COMMON SHARE 
* BOARD ALSO APPROVED A SPECIAL ONE-TIME CASH DIVIDEND PAYMENT OF $0.25 PER COMMON SHARE 
* QTRLY NET INTEREST INCOME $64.9 MILLION VERSUS ABOUT $59 MILLION Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
